Check	        Description
Is Empty	    Tree has no nodes
Is Leaf     	Node has no children
Is Full	        Each node has 0 or 2 children
Is Complete	    All levels filled except possibly last
Is Perfect	    All internal nodes have 2 children & leaves at same level
Is Balanced	    Height difference â‰¤1 (AVL condition)
Is BST	        Valid Binary Search Tree
Is Heap	        Valid Heap property
Is Symmetric	Mirror image tree
Is Skewed	    All nodes have only one child

Operation	            Description
Find Parent	            Parent of a node
Find Children	        Children of a node
Find Siblings	        Nodes with same parent
Find Ancestors	        All ancestors of a node
Find Descendants	    All children, grandchildren, etc.
Lowest Common Ancestor (LCA)	Common ancestor closest to nodes
